Class SensorWayPoint

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jdesktop.beans.AbstractBean
      • org.jdesktop.swingx.mapviewer.Waypoint
        • gui.maps.SensorWayPoint

  • public class SensorWayPoint
extends org.jdesktop.swingx.mapviewer.Waypoint
    This class corresponds to a sensor Waypoint on the map, with an associated hubness and bad hubness value, calculated from the sensor streams beforehand.
